<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Your insurance policy is due to renew on {!Opportunity.Policy_Inception_Date__c}.<br></b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b>Unfortunately </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">we have been unable to process the payment for your renewal</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. We used the details provided last year to take this payment.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Please call our renewals team on 01242 808 740 (option 2)</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> so we can update our records and renew your insurance.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Alternatively, reply to this email with a time, date and telephone number and we will schedule a call back to process your renewal.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>Please note, for security reasons we cannot accept card details sent to us via email.<br></i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><i><br></i>If we are unable to proceed with the payment, you risk a lapse in cover.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>